name: Return Message To Vul
description: After humanity discovered the alien species Vul and their everchanging Mothership; Vul'os, now they were trying to find out what was the ship transmitting. This footage was  taken with the rest of the transmission, it's encrypted but this was the best our team could do. It seems like Vul are not enemies, rather they are glad to find confirmations of life outside their own planet, just like us.
